<example xml:id="eg_dihedral_geom">
<title>Dihedral geometry</title>
<statement>
<p>
Fix an integer <m>n\geq 3</m>, and let <m>r,s\in D_n</m> be as defined in <xref ref="th_dihedral"/>. 
<ol>
    <li>
        <p>
            Give a precise geometric description of each rigid motion <m>r^is^j\in D_n</m>. 
        </p>
    </li>
    <li>
        <p>
            Let <m>s'=r^is</m> for any <m>1\leq i\leq n-1</m>. Prove that 
            <me>
                D_n=\{r^i(s')^j\mid 0\leq i\leq n-1, 0\leq j\leq 1\}
            </me>
            and that <m>s'</m> satisfies 
            <me>
                s'r=r^{-1}s'=r^{n-1}s'
